\id 2TI Kyaka Enga Shorter Bible, SF codes August 20, 93 
\h 2 TIMOTI 
\toc1 2 TIMOTI 
\toc2 2 Timoti 
\toc3 2 Tim 
\mt1 2 TIMOTI  
\ip Pole baa andapae dokome banya role pyao yulu pyuo nyiso pingi akali parange Timoti lenge doko dopa pyuo karare dapa pyuo karare lao nyiso pii lao pepa pase lapo pyao maiya. Renge angi doko Timoti baa maka nao yulu poraiyuo pyuo karena leya. Poleme Timoti mona porainyi pyambuo baa Yesu Koraisana lao pii polo lalana elya nao karena lamaiya. Pii angi Waili Pii Keyange dokonape Buku Baepole Ole Tesamene dokonape pyasi palenge dupwa minyuo karena lamaiya. Wambu dupwame baa pyalana pyuo randa maiyuo kararaminyipape Anatunya pii mana lao kata papyuo misi lao waili pii keyange doko polo lamaiyuo karena lamaiya.  
\ip Pii wakale wakale lao yanda pii nana lao Poleme Timoti repe repe pii lamaiya. Pii dopale dokome wambu nyisa napala serami wambu dupwa mee kokwa serasa pingi.  
\ip Poleme Timoti kando karo namba pinginyili pyuo pinya lamaiya. Poleme Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mona reto maka nao kare kare soo yulu poraiyuo pyuo karo wambu randa maiyaminyipa baa randa nao kareyamo doko suu pyao Timoti dopako pinya lamaiya.  
\iot Buku Dakena Pii Palamo Dusipa  
\io1 1. Pii kanda soo leya \ior 1:1-2\ior*  
\io1 2. Timoti kando lakando mona porainyi pyambuo pii leya \ior 1:3—2:13\ior*  
\io1 3. Dopa piri lao repe repe pii lamaiya \ior 2:14—4:15\ior*  
\io1 4. Pole baa apa pyuo karo lao Timoti lamaiya \ior 4:16-18\ior*  
\io1 5. Pii lao oto leya \ior 4:19-22\ior*  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Namba Pole Koraisa Yesunya aposele akali Anatu pipili lao suu piyamuli pyuo mapanyi nembeyamopa Anatumi lete karenge nyerami lalu lao leyamo dokona Koraisa Yesumoo nyuo pakao karamano.   
\p
\v 2 Nambana mona retenge wane Timoti emba keta pepa dake pyao jilyu. Rakane Anatu namwana Kamongo Koraisa Yesupana mona keyange palyuo ipingipi sakao nyiso karenge mona kyuu lao singipi emba keta palena lao leto.   
\s1 Anatu Kando Ange Lao Banya Yulu Dokona Pinya Lao Porainyi //  Pyambuo Lenge  
\p
\v 3 Nambana rora ambasupimi Anatu lakando mona suu pinginya pyapi pyuo soo lenge dokona namba opetaeko piyaminyili pyuo pipala eŋa pupyamopa Anatu sangyu lao karo. Yuu peparae kukwa korakamape ateŋa lao dokopa embena lao suu pyao Anatu sangyu lao lapa pilyu.  
\v 4 Namba embena ee leene dupwa suu pyapala kandapulimi kumulyu dokona epo emba kandapala dokopa raeme kumaro.  
\v 5 Namba embame Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao mandeene doko angi ingilyamo lao kame see nalyo. Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi dokore embena apusingi Loisa endakinyi Yunisapame opetae suu pyao peteyambipya. Doko suu pyao embena doko mendare ingyuo pelyamo lao silyu.  
\v 6 Dokona lao misi andake dokona nambame emba kingi nyuo rombo palyiyunupa Anatumi banya yulu emba keta jiyamo doko isasa pinyi pyambuo karape lao langilyu.  
\v 7 Anatumi Imambu jiyamo dokome pakange renge doko jinginde daa. Pakange renge jilyuŋi lao dokopa porainya rengepe mona retengepe range rapu pyuo karengepe dupwa Imambumi joo simbungi.   
\p
\v 8 Namwana Kamongo dokona pii polo lalana elya nao dee namba banya ingyuo karapusi palo dokona lapala elya nyii napipiyoko. Dopa pyuo Anatu emba porainyi pyambwaramopa waili pii keyange dokona lao randa emba keta eparamo epena rao laoko karape.  
\v 9 Baame namwa lete wai pyao nyepala banya ingyarami lao kyakale leya. Doko namwame range yulu keyange piyamande daa. Baa rangena suu piyamuli pyuo mona keyange palyuo ipyapala kyakale lao rombo palyiya. Yuu ene wasaroŋo lao karo dokopa Koraisa Yesu keta mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko joo kaeya.  
\v 10 Namwana Lete Wai Pyao Nyingi akali Koraisa Yesu baa epo panapala Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko baa keta paneya. Koraisame kumunginya rengena porainya renge namwa keta palenge doko nyuo anameya. Anamo waili pii keyange dokome kuma nange renge doko nyuo nolakaya.   
\p
\v 11 Anatumi namba aposele yulupi mana lenge yulupi dolapona waili pii keyange polo lare lao rombo palyiya.  
\v 12 Renge dokona lao namba keta randa nyilyu. Randa nyipunupape namba dokona lao elya nalyo. Nambame akali kapa ingingi lao suu pyao karo doko range silyu. Yuu gii mupwa ene pyaka sepa naramopa yulu piri lao rombo palyakaya dokona minyuo pyuo kararo dokopa kyawa minyuo karara.  
\v 13 Pii langiyunuli pyuo piri lao pii angi langiyu dupwa minyuo karape. Koraisa Yesupa pakaro karaminyi dokona Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retengepe dolapo poraiyuo minyuo pyuo karalu karare.  
\v 14 Imambu Poo Pyasi namwa maralyiyamo dokome emba nyisaramopa renge keyange emba keta palamo doko sakao sakao pyuo minyuo karape.   
\p
\v 15 Yuu Esia wambu peparaeme namba yaki nyiyami dokopa Piselasa Emosenisapa opetaemeko yaki nyiyambi doko emba silinyi.  
\v 16 Onisimasa namba yuu malu mee rae mainyi pyambuyamo dokona Kamongome banya ree palu sakao pyuo nyinya. Baame namba karapusi kareyo dokona elyapala kaeya naya.  
\v 17 Dopa pyuo karo baa yuu Orome epapala dokopa namba kaeya nao karapala kando nyiya.  
\v 18 Yuu gii mupwa pyaka seramopa Kamongo dokome Onisimasa baa sakao nyiso karena lao suu pilyu. Embame nambana lao yuu Epesasa dokona Onisimasame yulu andake pyakaya doko ama soo gisasi karene.   
\c 2  
\s1 Emba Randa Nyerene Dokona Pii Lapo  
\p
\v 1 Nambana wane Timoti emba Koraisa Yesupa pakao karo baa mona keyange palyapala ipyuo kararamopa porayapala karape.  
\v 2 Wambu malu soo kareyaminyipa lao kareyo pii dupwa emba soo gisii kande dupwa embame wambu mona palenge dupwa lamairinyipa nakama soo nyepala wambu wakale lamairami dokona mana lamaiyuo karape.\fig Akali aminya yulu pingi dupwa yulu wakalena minyuo komonda nange.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="2:4" \fig*   
\p
\v 3 Koraisa Yesunya yanda pyakamaingi akali ingyuo yasoko nao karare ingilyamo.  
\v 4 Akali aminya yulu pingi dupwa yulu wakalena minyuo komonda nange. Baa aminya yulu dokona yeelyo ami rapu pingi akali mupwa doko rae mainyi pyambuo pingi.  
\v 5 Akali bange nyelana makandenge baame makandengena lowa dupwa minya napala dokome bange nyuo kapa wini larande daa.  
\v 6 Ee wara pingi akalimi randa nao yulu poraiyuo piramo dokome ee mupwasa doko manjo nara ingilyamo.  
\v 7 Namba pii langilyu dupwa apa pyuonde lao suu pyao pisirinyipa Kamongome epapala nyisaramo dokopa kapa rolo sere.   
\p
\v 8 Yesu Koraisa Dapitinya para pyasi baa kumuo palyuo lopo epeyamo dokona waili pii keyange nambame lao karo doko suu pyaoko karape.  
\v 9 Namba waili pii keyange lapunu dokona lao randa nyipunupa wambu pingi akali dopale ingyuo puu saneme kiimbwaminyi karo. Dopa piminyipape Anatunya pii doko puu maiyuo retarami ingya nalyamo.  
\v 10 Dokona lao Anatunya rombo palyisi wambunya reke lao randa peparae nyuo karapusa pilyamo. Doko Koraisa Yesumi nakama opetae lete nyakaramopa yanga paupau lenge panda dokona karalu kararami lao randa nao karo.  
\v 11 Pii dake angingyuo letamo lao soo nyimana.  
\q1 Namwa Yesu kumuyamo dokona kumuyamande ramo doko  
\q1 baa lete karamuli pyuo karamwasa pilyamo.   
\q1
\v 12 Namwa Anatunya yulu reto kaeya nao pyuo kararama ramo doko  
\q1 baapa role pyao iso kararamasa pira.  
\q1 Banya kingi reto kaeyarama ramo doko  
\q1 baame namwana kingi reto kaeyarako.   
\q1
\v 13 Namwame banya yulu au pyuo rape rape lao pii nao karamanopape  
\q1 baame namwa yaki nyii nara.  
\q1 Baa rolae dupwa renge kuiyuo pyuo karenge dokome  
\q1 alowa pipala kopetame pira ingya nalyamo.   
\s1 Yulu Mora Piso Pingi Dokona Pii Lapo  
\p
\v 14 Pii dakeme embena wambu dupwa dee kamba mana lamairi. Dopa pyuo Anatunya kingi lao nakama pii wakale wakaleme minyuo yanda pii nana lao lamaipi. Pii dopale dokome wambu nyisa napala, serami wambu dupwa kokwa serasa pingi.  
\v 15 Emba yulu poraiyuo pipala Anatunya lenge kambu dorena angi yulu pingi wambuŋu lao kandaraminyi karape. Yulu akali angimi rangena yulu dupwana elya nyii nange. Dopale ingyuo Anatunya waili pii doko rolae mana lamairi.  
\v 16 Anatunya daa mee kopyali pii larami dokome Anatunya kata dupwana rekya lao paramili dopale dupwana wanjo karape.  
\v 17 Nakamame mana lamairami doko rete andake minjunya pipala ipwange nao isa ingyuo kulimbungi dopale. Aimeniasa Pailitasapa dolapo dokona mana lao karambinyi.  
\v 18 Nakama pii kinyi angi rolae lenge kata doko yaki nyepala wambu wambo kumuyami dupwa lopo neta epapeyami lao kyambo lao karaminyi. Nakambana pii dopale dokome akali lapona Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko ipwa palyinyi nembo lamisa pilyamo.  
\v 19 Dopa laminyipape Kurisene yulu doko Anatumi kanda soo piyamo doko ama porai wakasa ingyaro karamo dokome isa paa nara. Dokona pii dasipa pyasi palamo. Kamongo baame apimoo banya lao soo karamo. Mendeme, Namba Kamongona karo lara ramo doko baa koo dupwana rekya lanyi nembo kararasa pira.   
\p
\v 20 Anda andake dokona pete sanapengepe rara wakale wakale dupwa singi. Dokona lapo golope kana kulingipimi wasisi dee lapo isape yuupimi wasisi dupwa singi. Lapo ama yapasi ingilyamosa mee langa nyuo yulu pii nange. Lapome meeŋe lapala dokome andakarena yulu pingi.  
\v 21 Dokona suu pyao mendeme range waso poo pyasi ingyuo karara ramo doko baa yulu yapasi dupwana pira. Kamongo Anatumi baa rombo palyapala banya yulu mupwa lapo dupwa opetaeko pyakana lara ingilyamo. Dokona lao yulu keyange peparaena kapa pira ingilyamo.  
\v 22 Wanyane wambu keta suu pingi koo palamo doko wanjo yulu rolae doko anjuku lao pyuo Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pingipi mona retengepe mona kyuu lao singipi dusipana ingyuo pyuo karape. Doko wambu mona yapasi paliramo Kamongo nyisinya lao ateŋa lenge dupwamoo pipya karo. Dopako pyuo kararami ramo doko kapa ingyara.  
\v 23 Angi see nange kopyali dupwame laiya lapala apiyanda pyuo pyakandarami ingilyamo doko silinyi. Emba dopaleko ingya napipi.  
\v 24 Kamongona kendemande akali dupwame pyakandarami ingya nara. Baame wambu pipya anjiki pyuo mana lenge akali keyange ingyuo elya kalo pyuo karena.  
\v 25 Baa akali kamba lao karenge dupwa kando anjiki koo pyuo nakamana yulu kyai pilyaminyi dupwa lao rolakamirasa pira. Baame kamba lenge dupwa kando anjiki pyuo lara ramo dokopa Anatumi kata wapwakamiramopa nakama mona kapu kyuo pii angi doko serami ingyara.  
\v 26 Dokopa Sataneme nakama rambu lapala banya kame dokona karapusi kareyamo dupwa kingi rekya lapala kapu kyuo eparamisa pira.   
\c 3  
\s1 Yuu Gii Lumwa Piramo Dokona Pii Lapo  
\p
\v 1 Yuu gii lumwa pinya piramo dokopa randa wakale wakale dupwa epara ingilyamo doko soo karape.  
\v 2 Akali peparae rango nao bange nyipuli nyipuli lao suu pyao rangena kingi lakando moŋokyaŋe soo pii koo keta palyuo lao endangi rakangepena pii see nao sangyu laa nao Anatunya kingi kokwa sili lao kararami.  
\v 3 Wambu yango kilya kando karo yango mendali saka nao yango mata kando yulu koona wangu lako karo pyakando pyuo pyao yulu keyange dupwa isa nembo kararami.  
\v 4 Nakamana puu minyingi dupwa nyuo yanda pimwai keta mairami. Mondo lao range wasa nao mee langa karapala moŋokyaŋena renge dokome palyuo pyoko pyoko laramo kararami. Yanengena rae maingi dupwa mona nyepala Anatu mona reta narami lyakande.  
\v 5 Anatunya kata angi dokona mee pele lao yongona mamba kiso karapala banya porainya renge doko mata mairami. Wambu dopale dupwa waso karape.  
\v 6 Akali dupwana lapome enda mona pali nange dupwana andana papala kyambo lengenyili pyuo lao enda dupwa anamasi minyingi. Enda dopale dupwana koona renge palipyamo dupwame nyaa nyaa pupyasa punduo petaminyi.  
\v 7 Enda dupwa yuu peparae mana rolae nyelana piminyipape angi pii kinyi doko see nalyaminyi.  
\v 8 Akali Janisa dee Jambarisapame Mosesena pii sepala kamba leyambinyili pyuo akali dupwame pii angi doko sepala kamba lao karaminyi. Nakambana suu pingi rolo see nalyamosa kapa ingingi lao suu pingi doko isa penge.  
\v 9 Janisa Jambarisapa kopyali ingyuo kareyambinyi wambu peparaeme siyami doko suu pyao akali yulu koo doko pyuo karaminyi dupwana yulu repetale isa para ingilyamo.   
\s1 Anatunya Pii Poraiyuo Minyuo Karape  
\p
\v 10 Embame nambana yulu rolae pyuo karo dupwa soo nyepala moko minyuo pilinyi. Namba Anatu kapa ingingi lao suu pyao maka napala mana lao karo wambu yango mona reto pyuo kareyonopa  
\v 11 randa andake nyiyu dupwa kandee. Namba yuu Andioko Aikoniuma Lisatape randa andake wakasa nyepala au palyuo kara nayo doko emba siiyako. Dopa pyuo randa nyiyunupape Kamongome namba kiiramo nyiya.  
\v 12 Wambu peparae Koraisa Yesunya arapu dokona Anatunya Imambunya yulu pinya mona nyilyaminyi dupwa randa nyerami lyakande.  
\v 13 Satane akali Anatunya yulu pii lao mee karenge akali dupwame yulu koo pyuo pao kamame koo wakasa dokona pirami. Wambu mendali kando dereke pii lami dokona nakama range keta lao nyuo lamisa pilyamo.  
\v 14 Pii emba mana langiyaminyi soo nyiinyi dupwa minyuo karare. Doko apimoome mana langiyami lao range soo karene.  
\v 15 Emba wamba wane dokopa buku Baepole pii poo pyasi doko mana nyii kande. Pii dokome emba singinya renge joo Koraisa Yesu kapa ingingi lao suu pyarenepa lete wai pyao nyera.  
\v 16 Buku Baepole pii peparae Anatu keta epenge. Dokome pii kinyi dokona mora pisinyi pyambuo pii kyai dupwana lasaka pyuo pingi. Yulu kopetame dupwana lao nyuo rolapala apa pyuo rolae pyuo kararama lao mana lenge.  
\v 17 Dopa pyuo Anatunya yulu pyakamaingi wambu dupwame mana nyepala yulu keyange dupwana mora piso pyulu pyuo pirami.   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1-2 Koraisa Yesumi wambu kumasi dee lete karaminyi dupwa peparae kote lara dokope dee Anatunya lenge kambu dokonape nambame emba poraiyuo dopa pyuo langilyu. Yesu Koraisa baa pano epapala Kiŋi ingyuo karalu kararamo dokona banya waili pii doko wambu dupwa polo lamaipi. Yuu gii rolae doko pyaka serape panda see nara doko mupwa daaŋa lao emba lamaiyuoko karape. Yesunya pii dokona kinyi letene lao suu pinya lao pyalana pyuo lamaiyuo wambu porainyi pyambuo nakamana koo dupwa pano lamaiyuo pyuo karalu karare.  
\v 3 Renge pii kinyi doko kale yukupala see narami lyakande. Nakama pii angi kinyi doko soo nyii napala rangena suu pingi dokona moko minyuo mana lenge akali rangeme rombo palyapala pii wakale wakale dupwa mana langinya lao kararami.  
\v 4 Nakama pii angi doko yaki nyepala sinju pii wakale wakale dupwa kale yukupala lao soo kararami.  
\v 5 Dopa piraminyipape emba yuu peparae rangeme kame pyuo minyuo karare. Randa eparamopa mee pyuoko karo waili pii keyange dokona mondo lao lenge akali ingyuo Anatunya kendemande akali ingyuo karo embena yulu peparaena elya pyuo pyuo karare.\fig Yole rolaena kyawa rarange doko Kamongo dokome yuu gii mupwa eparamo dokopa jera.|src="FILEFIG" size="col" ref="4:8" \fig*   
\p
\v 6 Emba pyuo karare doŋo nambana yuu gii otara doko repetale pyaka sepelyamo. Namba Anatunya yulu dokona reke lao kumuo mairulyamo.  
\v 7 Namba range porayapala makandalana suu piyunu yuu dokona kaeya nao pao otapu. Imambunya yulu keyange dupwa nyelana lao suu pyao makando puu pao pupu.  
\v 8 Dopa pyuo pupunu dokona pyuo wini lapala yole nyero ingyaro silyamo. Yole rolaena kyawa rarange doko Kamongo kote pii rolae singi dokome yuu gii mupwa eparamo dokopa jera. Nambako iki jerande daa. Wakale lapo opetae baa epelyape lao mona reto iso karaminyi dupwana opetae ingyara.   
\s1 Pii Nakama Iki Kanjinginya Palyuo Langirowale  
\p
\v 9 Emba range porayapala waiya lao namba kandala epare.  
\v 10 Akali Dimasa baa isa yuunya bange rae maipala namba yaki nyepala yuu Tesalonaika dokona peya. Akali Kurisene doko baa yuu Galasia peya. Dee Taitesa baa yuu Dalamesia dokona peya.  
\v 11 Luku iki dae karamo. Embame Make nyepala dae lanyuo epare. Eparambinyipa Makeme Anatunya yulu pyuo namba kapa nyisara.  
\v 12 Akali Tikikasa yuu Epesasa pena leyo.  
\v 13 Emba dae epana dokopa nambana komau pee pingi andake yuu Toasa range Kapasana andana yaki nyiyunu doko minyakao ipupi. Dopa pyuo epo dokopa nambana buku dupwa opetae minyakao epo dokopa buku kuki namba rangena pii pyao palyingi dusipa kame see napipi.   
\p
\v 14 Ane kapa wasingi akali Alekesanda dokome namba randa andake jiya. Baa apa pyuo piya lao Kamongome yano pyara.  
\v 15 Baa waili pii lao kareyama dokona imbu singi mandeya dokona emba range baapa kandokondali pyuo karape.   
\p
\v 16 Namba kanda soo kote leyami dokopa mendeme nambana lao nyisapa nayami. Mee peparaeme namba yaki nyuo kaeyami. Anatumi nakamana koo piyami dokona suu pyao kaeyakaminya leto.  
\v 17 Dopa piyaminyipa Yesumi namba role pyao karapala banya porainya renge jiya. Jiyamo dokona waili pii angi doko lamaiyunupa Juu daa rara wakale dupwa peparae kapa siyami. Mende doko namba mena laenena nenge kata dokona Anatu baame nenge raka lao nyiya.  
\v 18 Kamongome namba yulu koo dupwana kingi raka lanyi nembo banya yake panda iso karenge dorena mondo lao lanyuo para. Dokona lao banya kingi doko neta renge ingyuo sulu sinya, doko kinyi.   
\s1 Pii Lao Oto Yako Lenge Pii  
\p
\v 19 Pirisila Akuilapa yako lao dokopa Onesiporasana ree palu opetae yako leto.  
\v 20 Irasatasa yuu Korina dokona karo kaeyamopa, Topimasa baa anga piyamosa yuu Mailitasa dokona yaki nyiyu.  
\v 21 Emba kupwa pingi pyaka sepa naramo dokopa wambo ipulinya suu pyao karape.  
\p Yupyulasamoo, Pyutenesa, Lainasa, Kolotiamoo dee lapo dupwa opetaeme yako letaminyi.   
\p
\v 22 Kamongome nakama pipya role pyao kararamopa Anatunya mona keyange palyuo ipingi doko nakama keta palena.   